{"tid":1883641,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"謝拉特：一直關注曼城事件","createTime":"2020-02-17T05:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T09:07:19.000Z","uid":20611,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"59f78ef7da7bca3d966538171521f9c8d822b697","tid":1883641,"uid":20611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"日前有報導指曼城受罰一事亦可能影響英超，更有報導指 2012 至 2016 年間違規的曼城有機會被褫奪期間贏得的冠軍，謝拉特向《每日郵報》表示非常關注事件：「我今早（昨天）看到了新聞，從歐洲足協的角度，這是很嚴重的判罰。」<br />\n<br />\n「我肯定他們（曼城）會上訴，所以還是等著看吧，然後我們可看看英超賽會怎處理。」<br />\n<br />\n「我會在得知英超賽會的動作後才評論。但你見到歐洲足協的判罰嚴重程度，可估計已發生了很大的錯誤。我對這樁事件的結果很感興趣，但在英超賽會判決前我不會說甚麼。」<br />\n<br />\n「但我真的很感興趣，原因很明顯吧。」"},{"pid":"91a2211244fee9b7686b754b1ea308fa930af914","tid":1883641,"uid":5652,"like":31,"dislike":37,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"呢條柒頭皮成個乞衣咁\\<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},{"pid":"256b474e480c68612a2667f7828bb1de1ec84d91","tid":1883641,"uid":308486,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"遲黎的冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51ff159d7297930f802089ce53ba2cd1e39e39c","tid":1883641,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"謝4:今次真係唔會再slip"},{"pid":"c669119b4d0e229d34c51ddf632de127abeeff73","tid":1883641,"uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/Zv2bfXO.gif\" />"},{"pid":"447794bc19da94ffc23c7bc9298d3bc4d52229e8","tid":1883641,"uid":204985,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"謝拉特:一直關注事件，希望曼城球員同球迷盡早轉會，天祐曼城！"},{"pid":"082d0da529324e20df1c7081fbef12f112512453","tid":1883641,"uid":3747,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"真兄弟明既就明"},{"pid":"dcf4af6b5034a58040911385704b0a06a4cc20c1","tid":18836